"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"在国内使用Discord软件会出现一些意想不到的问题，有不少朋友在每次启动Discord客户端的时候，总是会卡在如下图所示的Checking For Updates检查更新页面：\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/-KsqIsr_u3Q7zoLJtR92e.png?height=585&width=620)\\n\\n要不就是过一会出现Update Failed - Retrying in 30 SEC的提示，意思是更新失败将在30秒后重试，然后又返回检查更新的界面。\\n\\n出现这种现象的原因是Discord在国内的网络连接受到“干扰”造成的，我是这样解决的。\\n\\n首先将Checking For Updates检查更新的窗口关闭，然后将系统代理设置为全局模式，接着再重新启动Discord客户端，就OK了。\\n\\n参考教程：[Discord启动后卡在Checking For Updates界面的解决方法](https://520555.xyz/discord-checking-for-updates-stuck/)\",\"timestamp\":1637414730,\"title\":\"Discord Checking For Updates卡住怎么办\"},\"digest\":\"gPmLjUe44yLMPbOSJnun8ne42mrvRPLMuXvvXuGykhI\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x35DC13D8E143dE9d20FCeE8206F8fB30960417f9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hTd4fisCaXJnfrfn2Afhrd2WFA7xlT7gO3PzczJ4LuA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"PkfxVHYOBWiJyLqDKlv1AAu7obe456eRWXv2OyPsibk\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"WM4MXLgzdiW13iwiuGbhnxRDlnJBadxBWSpgj6qM0TT1BUVX5Par7bWNavw-KsZhA3fsK0wV-y2aFwALGLGuBA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x35cbedd555e9c6bddcdaa98cfa8bc724ec683821883ab50b2a9e263593877ade2c467e7c4ca81cf98842fdd8b3afaf3d285b0e77a812b65b45eca0a39aad41501b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"hTd4fisCaXJnfrfn2Afhrd2WFA7xlT7gO3PzczJ4LuA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"PkfxVHYOBWiJyLqDKlv1AAu7obe456eRWXv2OyPsibk\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"pOLKOJqEP6uRz6xC3OuJLWrvWhFfEh1iX6bU8J0WETE\"}"